            <ul class="list-group">
                <li class="list-group-item" style="background-color:#FAFBFC;font-weight:bold">付费SDK列表</li>
                <li class="list-group-item">[工业控件库] <a style="cursor:pointer;color:#357CE2" href="https://github.com/dathlin/HslControlsDemo">HslControls</a><img class="pull-right" title="star" src="https://img.shields.io/github/stars/dathlin/HslControlsDemo.svg?style=social&amp;label=Stars" alt="star" width="82" height="20"></li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

